// Contracts compiled using 0.8.20 (txCreateContract)
// the contract source code

contract Storage {
    address public owner;
    string str;

    constructor(string memory input) {
        owner = msg.sender;
        str = input;
    }

    function get() external view returns (string memory) {
        return str;
    }
}

end

account_new acc1 4467389

# deploy contract compiled with 0.8.20
transaction_build txCreateContract
    sender acc1
    receiverAddress 00
    value 0
    data 
    gas 4467389
    build

block_build b01
    parent g00
    gasLimit 6500000
    transactions txCreateContract
    build

block_connect b01

# Assert best block
assert_best b01

# check sender balance, it should pay the total cost of contract creation WITH initcode size cost
assert_balance acc1 0
